notes.title: **Outback Event**
points: - - The Didgeridollar cap has been raised from 3500 to 6500!
- - The rate at which Didgeridollars are earned has been increased alongside a week extension of the event!
- One final secret nameplate for the Outback Event is now unlockable in game, happy hunting!

notes.title: **Outback Species**
points: - The size of the new Outback species have been adjusted to be unique from each other.

notes.title: **Activities**
points: - Slightly buffed activity experience gain from golfing.

notes.title: **Misc**
points: - You can no longer catch the T.A.P. fishing background more than once while fishing.
- Fixed a district reset issue with the Trolley during the Trolley Tracks holiday.
- Added a significant amount of words to the whitelist.
